<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1467000' id='t-1467000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1469000' id='t-1469000'>Yeah, good. Yeah.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1471000' id='t-1471000'>You can take the nostril too, because some guys think --</span>
